[Civ. No. 7361. First Appellate District, Division One. February 16, 1931.] In the Matter of the Guardianship of the Estate of MADS NIELSEN, an Incompetent Person. GEORGE F. WITTER, Appellant, v. MADS NIELSEN, an Incompetent Person, etc., Respondent.

George F. Witter, in pro. per., for Appellant.

W. E. Most for Respondent.

THE COURT.

Appeal from an order fixing attorney’s fees in the estate of an incompetent.

The order is affirmed on authority of Estate of Nielsen, ante, p. 744 [296 Pac. 122], this day decided.
